{"tid":2401240,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「中美友好」 北京向拜登示好 遭侵權的New Balance獲判賠巨款","createTime":"2021-02-09T14:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T16:32:30.000Z","uid":310867,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e6652b5db0be6f0b0647ef176e85e27801bfa0","tid":2401240,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:34:41.000Z","msg":"在美國總統拜登剛就任，北京當局試圖修復與華府緊繃關係之際，上海市黃埔區人民法院上個月判決，模仿美國體育用品製造商新百倫（New Balance）傾斜的N商標的中國2家公司，<span class=\"red\">必須賠償2500萬元人民幣（以下同，約新台幣1.1億元），為外國品牌在中國提起商標侵權官司中，獲判賠的史上最高金額。</span><br />\n<br />\n竊取智財權一直是美中貿易緊張的主因。成都德恒律師事務所商標保護合夥律師吳宇恒表示：「北京當局已送出1個強烈的訊號，<span class=\"red\">中國是很認真的在保護智財權，這是吸引外資的關鍵，尤其是中國亟需外資之際。」</span><br />\n<br />\n被告的2家廠商分別是福建的製鞋商New Barlun和其經銷商上海Shiyi Trade，他們販售仿冒新百倫的運動鞋，但售價卻不到正品的一半，靠此方式在中國小型城市迅速擴張。<br />\n<br />\n新百倫是在2016年首度採取法律行動，控告數十家中國仿冒廠商，去年4月初獲勝訴，當時上海市浦東新區人民法院裁定，New Barlun必須就非法使用新百倫的N商標，賠償新百倫1080萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3437200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3437200&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=9a19f80f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3437200&h=e5acaf08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3437200</a>"},{"pid":"ea46438380aa749f3f418638500c60a37d2672f6","tid":2401240,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/PZd59oglW6o/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FPZd59oglW6o%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=45d2a8ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ntdtv.com.tw/public/uploads/assets/2017/04/19/2017-04-19-58f770102771c-780x571-13196.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com.tw%2Fpublic%2Fuploads%2Fassets%2F2017%2F04%2F19%2F2017-04-19-58f770102771c-780x571-13196.jpg&h=07dc7b29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05815199c7f63a29913e67e7ef6688c0f8bca3a1","tid":2401240,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:39:34.000Z","msg":"北韓式人治社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a68473efafd2fd25ac2b20aeb31d650fb0c1b9c","tid":2401240,"uid":123738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T16:32:30.000Z","msg":"支那偷野真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係班左膠先會繼續奶支那春袋"}]}